· Complete decision log
· Legal justification for each action
· Time-stamped evidence collection
· Independent verification capability

5.5 Human Oversight Integration

Human-machine collaboration framework:

Level 1: Autonomous Operation

· System operates independently
· Human monitoring only
· For low-risk, time-critical scenarios

Level 2: Human Confirmation

· System recommends action
· Human confirms or rejects
· 30-second response window

Level 3: Human Control

